author: J14T14
title: Dimensions Rip-off
review: Just by looking at the instructions and the overall look of the final build, I can see that this set is a direct copy of the LEGO Dimensions 71205 Jurassic World Team Pack build for Blue, except for the build for the arm and one part in the tail. For collectors, this can be a bit insulting and unappealing. The arms especially look worse that the dimensions build and should have at least been done in sand green. Overall, I do not recommend this set. You would probably be better off with the dimensions build than with this in-store build.
